Understanding Lattice
---------------------

Last September I interviewed Anduril Co-Founder and CEO Brian Schimpf ( htt=
ps://stratechery.com/2023/an-interview-with-anduril-founder-and-ceo-brian-s=
chimpf-about-software-and-the-military/?access_token=3DeyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIs=
